data.description: Lovingly maintained and barely lived in DR Horton built home in Fairway Farms. It features a brick and stone elevation and has 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths and a 3 car attached garage. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances including recent dishwasher, rich exotic counters and 42 inch ivory cabinets. Subway tile backsplash in herringbone pattern. 5 inch hickory hardwood flooring throughout much of the home excluding wet areas. On demand water heater and RO water softener Zoned to award-winning Tomball schools. A large one-story with a 3 car garage doesn't come on the market very often. Call while this home is still available.
